name: Lands
description:
This is a pair of women's pants from Lands' End in a size 10.
 These pants are light blue in color and feature a flat front, a mid-rise, two slash pockets, a button, bar hook and zipper front closure, two faux back pockets, and a straight leg style.
 These pants measure 16 across the waist with a 25 inseam and a 10.5 rise when laid flat. They were made in Sri Lanka of a 98/2 cotton/spandex blend.
 These pants are in good pre-owned condition with a couple of faint spot stains near the right leg opening.
